quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  6,9,Wa Law Ja`alnāhu Malakāan Laja`alnāhu Rajulāan Wa Lalabasnā `Alayhim Mā Yalbisūna
  6,10,Wa Laqadi Astuhzi'a Birusulin Min Qablika Faĥāqa Bial-Ladhīna Sakhirū Minhum Mā Kānū Bihi Yastahzi'ūn
  6,11,Qul Sīrū Fī Al-'Arđi Thumma Anžurū Kayfa Kāna `Āqibatu Al-Mukadhibīna
  6,12,Qul Liman Mā Fī As-Samāwāti Wa Al-'Arđi Qul Lillāhi Kataba `Alá Nafsihi Ar-Raĥmata Layajma`annakum 'Ilá Yawmi Al-Qiyāmati Lā Rayba Fīhi Al-Ladhīna Khasirū 'Anfusahum Fahum Lā Yu'uminūna
  6,13,Wa Lahu Mā Sakana Fī Al-Layli Wa An-Nahāri Wa Huwa As-Samī`u Al-`Alīmu
  6,14,Qul 'Aghayra Allāhi 'Attakhidhu Walīyāan Fāţiri As-Samāwāti Wa Al-'Arđi Wa Huwa Yuţ`imu Wa Lā Yuţ`amu Qul 'Innī 'Umirtu 'An 'Akūna 'Awwala Man 'Aslama Wa Lā Takūnanna Mina Al-Mushrikīna
  6,15,Qul 'Innī 'Akhāfu 'In `Aşaytu Rabbī `Adhāba Yawmin `Ažīmin
  6,16,Man Yuşraf `Anhu Yawma'idhin Faqad Raĥimahu Wa Dhalika Al-Fawzu Al-Mubīnu
  6,17,Wa 'In Yamsaska Allāhu Biđurrin Falā Kāshifa Lahu 'Illā Huwa Wa 'In Yamsaska Bikhayrin Fahuwa `Alá Kulli Shay'in Qadīrun
  6,18,Wa Huwa Al-Qāhiru Fawqa `Ibādihi Wa Huwa Al-Ĥakīmu Al-Khabīru